    "10 The present report presents the findings of the interviews conducted by Ithaka S+R and teams from our 19 cohort institutions during the spring of 2024.",
    "11 These interviews asked faculty, graduate students, and other individuals to reflect on their perceptions of and experiences with generative AI in both teaching and research contexts.",
    "While the full interview guide can be found in Appendix C, our study was driven by the following questions: To what degree are instructors and researchers adopting generative AI, and how is this changing their approaches and practices in teaching and research?",
    "What challenges are they facing in the aftermath of generative AI's emergence?",
    "What kinds of support have they benefited from, and what kinds of support do they still need?"
